com.chap.links.client

Class TimelineEntryPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chap.links.client.TimelineEntryPoint

  • public class TimelineEntryPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    TimelineEntryPoint Entry point classes define onModuleLoad(). The class TimelineEntryPoint is for test purposes. To run the program, you have to open the file Timeline.gwt.xml, and uncomment the line such that the entry point is defined. If you want to create a stand-alone module for the timeline, you have to comment the line with the entry point again, and then create a jar containing only Timeline.java, Timeline.gwt.xml, timeline.js, and timeline.css
